{"tid":1174461,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格攔截施丹！","createTime":"2019-05-28T00:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:57:48.000Z","uid":11081,"like":384,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"cffb240198ef9d67dc019ec08ce1dfeabecd518a","tid":1174461,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/05/28/8/887e6aa40df7dc62851814e0455bef2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F8%2F887e6aa40df7dc62851814e0455bef2e.jpg&h=e89f0f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在日前的一場慈善賽中，年近70歲的前阿仙奴教練雲格攜手皇馬教練施丹參賽，一同參加這場慈善賽的，還有法國教練迪甘斯、法國傳奇柏賓以及法國橄欖球名宿施巴斯坦-沙巴爾等人。<br />\n<br />\n  在這場慈善賽中，雲格和施丹分別代表不同的球隊征戰。在一次進攻中，施丹直傳，被「老將」雲格機敏攔截，但在雲格帶球後撤準備組織反擊時，施丹又上前逼搶成功，將球反斷了下來。<br />\n<br />\n  失球後的雲格明顯體力不支，放棄繼續跟防施丹，退回到禁區中防守，隨後施丹的傳中也如雲格所料被解圍。這一攻一防也讓場邊響起了善意的笑聲和掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，據現場球迷稱，雲格還在比賽中完成了一次「告魯夫轉身」，將施丹過了個干乾淨淨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/212/20190528/10207014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F212%2F20190528%2F10207014%2F&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=12ba6800\" target=\"_blank\">https://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/212/20190528/10207014/</a><br />\n<br />\n爺爺&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;光頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9ba36fada525e340941116f666df0b3dd08d98","tid":1174461,"uid":94739,"like":334,"dislike":1,"score":333,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:59:52.000Z","msg":"要70歲雲爺爺係咁跑<br />\n<br />\n虐老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86afce7bd2b03075db1adafd9508ee093cfbb223","tid":1174461,"uid":133787,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:03:06.000Z","msg":"真係驚佢出事"},{"pid":"31c34e13d489127d8a0b15677dfddb04161fd249","tid":